### User Profile Image API Test
### IntelliJ HTTP Client

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081
@userId = 14a80d8c-d021-70a9-ba28-5bab07c853c5
@userProfileDraftId = 660e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001

### ===========================================
### POST - Upload User Profile Image
### ===========================================

### Upload Profile Image - INFLUENCER / PROFILE
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user-profile
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="meta"; filename="meta.json"
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "userType": "INFLUENCER",
  "profileImageType": "PROFILE",
  "userProfileDraftId": "{{userProfileDraftId}}"
}
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test-profile.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test-profile.png
--boundary--

